      "description": "Offering an immaculate 2005 BMW M3 Competition Package (ZCP). This S54-powered icon features a high-revving 3.2L straight-six with factory individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically, the rod bearings and subframe have been inspected and verified to factory tolerances, ensuring structural integrity. The 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with the M-Variable limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its deep factory luster with zero paint imperfections, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. This specimen represents a reference-level example of BMW M\u2019s naturally aspirated pinnacle, free of any fluid seepage or bushing degradation. A turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
