      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop under any light. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. This is an investment-grade example that drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new machine. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
